title: Foo Fighters - Rio de Janeiro 2015
description:
The Rio de Janeiro presentation for the Foo Fighters - Sonic Highways tour, occurred at Maracana Stadium on Jan. 25, 2015, as transmitted by brazilian paid channel Multishow. 

There are minor transmission errors from the original video file here and there, but it is good quality overall. 

I took the whole thing, converted and splitted the MP3 files separately. Enjoy!
